，周润发感慨“很难相信这个是在中国盖的一个城市”。这座城不仅让白客感到“震撼”、带给张新成很强的沉浸感，也深深触动了饰演格兰特的好莱坞演员约翰·库萨克，他坦言自己从业多年来在美国和世界各地都拍过电影，但“我从未见过一个世界被创造得如此详细、精致、美丽、完美”。相信每位走进电影院的观众也必将会被剧组真实重现的1900年旧金山的风貌所震撼。"},"attached_info":"CkII8bawmPXW7KchEAMaCTExMzM2NDI1OSDsga29BjAAOLoBQBZyCzExOTQyMDc5NTg0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"58 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-c6f62339eaa879ded0a70d4a51545e31_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"23_1739478005.625406","card_id":"Q_12144718943","target":{"id":12144718943,"title":"《哪吒之魔童闹海》成为中国影史首部票房破 100 亿的电影，这百亿票房意味着什么？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/12144718943","type":"question","created":1739445037,"answer_count":434,"follower_count":759,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[68,23041,26606,771703,3836081],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"[图片]"},"attached_info":"CkII8bawmPXW7KchEAMaCTExMzQwNDg1NSCtpre9BjAAOPcFQBdyCzEyMTQ0NzE4OTQzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"57 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-050c52fe66d0e5e49822f78bc2cf9628_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"24_1739478005.626077","card_id":"Q_12073298413","target":{"id":12073298413,"title":"特朗普与俄、乌总统通电话，谈了「停战、互访、还钱」等话题，并称乌克兰加入北约不切实际，释放了什么信号？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/12073298413","type":"question","created":1739404110,"answer_count":480,"follower_count":925,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1234,30738,34688,136525,159978],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"美国东部时间2月12日，美国总统特朗普先后与俄罗斯总统普京、乌克兰总统泽连斯基通电话。这也是特朗普宣誓就职以来，首次与俄乌领导人通话。通话后，特朗普说，乌克兰加入北约不切实际。 综合克里姆林宫和白宫方面的消息，特朗普与